---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy | SaaS Pricing Toolkit" description="Cookie policy and consent preferences for this website.">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p>
      This site uses cookies (and similar storage) for analytics and advertising. Calculator inputs are processed in your
      browser and are not intentionally collected by this site.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="grid">
    <section class="card col8">
      <h2>What we use cookies for</h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li>Analytics: understand aggregated usage and improve the toolkit.</li>
        <li>Advertising: serve ads and measure performance.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">Your choices</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        You can accept or reject cookies via the banner. To change your choice later, use the "Cookie settings" link in
        the footer.
      </p>
      <p class="muted">
        Your preference is stored locally in your browser (key: <code>cookie_consent</code>). If you reject cookies, we do
        not grant analytics/ad storage (Google Consent Mode stays denied).
      </p>
    </section>
    <aside class="card col4">
      <h2>Note</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        If you target jurisdictions that require a certified consent management platform (CMP), integrate one before
        scaling traffic.
      </p>
    </aside>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
